ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This project uses data and code patterns from:

  Zimmer, A., Brooks, N., Gaughan, A. E., Tuholske, C. (2026).
  Global Divergence in Urban Demographic Change and Migration Patterns.
  Nature Cities.

  Original repository: https://github.com/zimmermaps/urban_demography
  Originally released under the MIT License.

The Global Urban Demographic Dataset (GUDD) and the original analysis code
were created by Zimmer et al. This project applies their methodology and
visualization style to a focused analysis of U.S. cities.
